sections.heading: Department; approve programs and materials
sections.text: The department shall approve all courses, lectures, seminars, course materials, or other instructional programs used to meet the requirements of sections 71-6038 to 71-6042.SourceLaws 1983, LB 273, ยง 3;Laws 1996, LB 1044, ยง 750;Laws 2004, LB 1005, ยง 112;Law
